	dprr:hasID 9601 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/9600> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #9600" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/10> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "ref. 469" ;
	dprr:hasID 9600 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5899> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5899" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Imperator of the Pompeian forces in Spain (see 46, Promagistrates), who was defeated at Munda and killed in the flight (Bell. Hisp., passim; Liv. Per. 115; Vell. 2.55.2-4; Suet. Iul. 35.2; 36; Plut. Caes. 56; App. BC 2.103-105; Flor. 2.13.76-87; Dio 43.29-40; Eutrop. 6.24; Auct. Vir. Ill. 78.8; Oros. 6.16.6-9; Zonar. 10.10; cf. Cic. Att. 12.37a; Fast. Caer., CIL 12.1, p. 212; Fast. Farn., ibid. p. 250; Strabo 3.2.2, and 4.9; Val. Max. 9.2.4; Plin. NH 3.12; 36.134; Lucan 1.40; Polyaen. 8.23.16)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5899 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5812> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5812" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "He assumed the title Imperator in Spain (Grueber, CRRBM 2.364-367; CIL 12.2.885; Bell. Hisp. 42.6, fasces imperiumque sibi arripuit), where he had arrived by early in 46 (see 47, Legates). He soon occupied Baetica, and rallied a force of thirteen legions (Cic. Att. 12.2.1; Auct. Bell. Hisp. 7.4; 30.1; Nic. Dam., Vit. Aug. 10, FGrH 2A.394f.; Vell. 2.55.2; Plut. Caes. 56.1; App. BC 2.87, and 103; Flor. 2.13.73-74; Dio 43.29-31). See D.-G. 4.562, no. 24." ;
	dprr:hasID 5812 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5770> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5770" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Sent on from Africa to rally Pompeian support in Spain, either m a Legatus or as a Promagistrate (Dio 42.56.3-4; cf. Cic. Att. 12.2.1; App. BC 2.87; Auct. Bell. Afr. 22-23; Bell. Hisp. 1.1; date uncertain, probably in 47). See D.-G. 4.5.62, no. 24; 3.516, and 566." ;
	dprr:hasID 5770 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5722> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5722" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Held command of the Egyptian section of Pompey's fleet, and burned some of Caesar's fleet at Oricum and Lissus (Caes. BC 3.40; Dio 42.12.1-4). Deserted by his fleet after Pharsalus, he went with Cato and the other Pompeian leaders to Africa (Caes. BC 3.111.3; Plut. Cic 39.1-2; Cat. Min. 55.3; Die 42.12.4; cf. App. BC 2.87, to Spain). See D.-G. 4.562, no. 24." ;
	dprr:hasID 5722 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5616> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5616" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Collected and commanded a squadron of Egyptian ships in his father's fleet (Caes. BC 3.4.4, and 5.3, and 111. 3; Plut. Ant. 25; Pomp. 62.2; App. BC 2.71). See D-G. 4.562, no 24." ;
	dprr:hasID 5616 .
